# Telegram Bot on Vercel

This is a simple Telegram bot built with Node.js and deployed on Vercel.

## Features
- Replies to user messages
- Built with Vercel serverless functions
- Uses Telegram Bot API

## Setup
1. Add BOT_TOKEN in Vercel Environment Variables
2. Deploy project
3. Set webhook to /api/webhook

## Webhook URL
https://your-domain.vercel.app/api/webhook
